&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a &lt;strong&gt;Mid-Level Data Engineer&lt;/strong&gt; to join our &lt;strong&gt;Revenue Operations&lt;/strong&gt; team, responsible for building, scaling, and maintaining data pipelines that support strategic revenue decisions.&lt;/p&gt;
