&lt;p data-start=&quot;61&quot; data-end=&quot;455&quot;&gt;The profile is a specialist in the Blip product who acts as both a technical consultant and a user experience consultant. &lt;br&gt;Their main activities include: presentations and hands-on demonstrations of the Blip platform, leading meetings to gather requirements (discovery and workshops), analyzing the feasibility of implementations, and designing solution proposals to achieve client objectives.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;457&quot; data-end=&quot;873&quot;&gt;You will work on finding a balance between the ideal user journey and the most efficient and feasible journey that can be built using Blip products. You will also interact with both the technical teams of our clients and the development and implementation teams of Blip products. For this, we expect you to understand the importance of teamwork, with a willingness to share knowledge, learn, and grow continuously.&lt;/p&gt;
