&lt;p data-start=&quot;974&quot; data-end=&quot;1028&quot;&gt;As a Data Analyst, your responsibilities will include:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul data-start=&quot;1030&quot; data-end=&quot;2493&quot;&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1030&quot; data-end=&quot;1260&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1032&quot; data-end=&quot;1260&quot;&gt;Creating, making available, evolving, and maintaining data products based on our clients’ business needs; designing, creating, and improving dashboards and custom scripts for advanced data analysis and business KPI monitoring.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1261&quot; data-end=&quot;1462&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1263&quot; data-end=&quot;1462&quot;&gt;Contributing to discussions on data storage and data pipelines to support advanced analytical reporting, as well as data analysis and exploration, using various data and visualization technologies.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1463&quot; data-end=&quot;1611&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1465&quot; data-end=&quot;1611&quot;&gt;Working closely with analytics engineers and data product managers to identify process improvements and align these changes with team practices.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1612&quot; data-end=&quot;1781&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1614&quot; data-end=&quot;1781&quot;&gt;Collaborating with stakeholders by providing guidance, data, and analytical support for the development of new analyses and tools that support strategic initiatives.&lt;/p&gt;
