&lt;li data-start=&quot;1934&quot; data-end=&quot;2018&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1936&quot; data-end=&quot;2018&quot;&gt;Encouraging and promoting DataOps practices in the development of data products.&lt;/p&gt;
