&lt;h2 data-start=&quot;2500&quot; data-end=&quot;2534&quot;&gt;Requirements&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;2536&quot; data-end=&quot;2564&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;2536&quot; data

&lt;div class=&quot;p-pdf_iframe__page&quot; data-page-number=&quot;1&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;textLayer&quot; data-main-rotation=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Estamos buscando um(a) profissional de compras para atuar no modelo híbrido em Belo Horizonte.&lt;br&gt;Conduzir a contratação estratégica de fornecedores para diversas categorias, garantindo o melhor custo-benefício (TCO), mitigação de riscos e cumprimento de SLAs, visando vantagens competitivas de longo prazo para a companhia.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;RESPONSABILIDADES E ATRIBUIÇÕES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;- Liderar negociações diversas e estabelecer acordos de longo prazo com&amp;nbsp;parceiros estratégicos.&lt;br&gt;- Avaliar o Total Cost of Ownership (TCO), considerando cenários financeiros, tributários e logísticos.&lt;br&gt;- Realizar análises técnicas: CBD (Cost Breakdown), Should Cost, Make or Buy e Spend Analysis.&lt;br&gt;- Atuar em projetos de redução de custos (Saving) e análise de valor.&lt;br&gt;- Desenvolver, homologar e acompanhar fornecedores (SRM - Supplier Relationship Management).&lt;br&gt;- Monitorar KPIs da área e fornecer insights para melhoria contínua.&lt;br&gt;- Analisar tendências de mercado, inovação e riscos para mitigar interrupções na cadeia de suprimentos.&lt;br&gt;- Definir metas e prazos estratégicos para garantir a agilidade e eficiência dos processos.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;textLayer&quot; data-main-rotation=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;REQUISITOS TÉCNICOS (HARD SKILLS)&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;- Formação: Ensino Superior Completo (ADM, Engenharia, Economia ou correlatas).&lt;br&gt;- Idiomas: Inglês ou Espanhol Avançado.&lt;br&gt;- Excel: Nível Avançado.&lt;br&gt;- Metodologias: Domínio de Strategic Sourcing,&lt;br&gt;- Experiência: Sólida vivência prévia em compras, preferencialmente com foco em Serviços.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PERFIL COMPORTAMENTAL (SOFT SKILLS)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;- Senso de Urgência: Priorização em ambiente de pressão constante por prazos.&lt;br&gt;- Ética e Compliance: Integridade inquestionável no trato com fornecedores.&lt;br&gt;- Flexibilidade e Resiliência: Agilidade para lidar com múltiplas tarefas e mudanças.&lt;br&gt;- Perfil Analítico e Ágil: Capacidade de atenção múltipla e olhar crítico sobre dados.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DIFERENCIAIS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;- Conhecimento em sistema SAP.&lt;br&gt;- Domínio de um segundo idioma estrangeiro.&lt;br&gt;- Pós-graduação em Supply Chain ou Gestão de Projetos&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Vantagens e benefícios&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Sua Experiência no Dia a Dia&lt;/strong&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;🕘&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Horário Flexível&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;: Mais autonomia para organizar sua rotina com equilíbrio e responsabilidade.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;🏠&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Modelos de Trabalho Flexíveis&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;: Remoto, híbrido ou presencial, conforme a necessidade da função.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;👕&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;No Dress Code&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;: Liberdade para ser quem você é, sem formalidades.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;🎉&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Day Off de Aniversário&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;: Um dia de folga no mês do seu aniversário para comemorar como quiser.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;🔋&amp;nbsp; Blip Recharge:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;São 5 dias de folga remunerados por ano, para cargos que não fazem registro de ponto, pensados ​​para equilibrar a jornada.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Bem-estar e Qualidade de Vida&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;🍽️&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Vale Alimentação ou Refeição&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;: R$ 1144,00 mensais, sem desconto e creditado inclusive nas férias e licenças.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;🚍&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Vale Transporte&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;: Disponível conforme necessidade de deslocamento.&lt;/l

&lt;p&gt;We are looking for someone to fill the position of&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Product Manager&lt;/strong&gt; at Blip, working in our &lt;em&gt;Professional Services&lt;/em&gt; unit. You will collaborate directly with the client, designing and delivering value to the business through the development and evolution of customer service chatbots, services and campaigns (conversational intelligence) within our BLIP platform.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be the strategic business leader within a technical team that develops and improves chatbots for clients in the Professional Services area. As a Service Product Manager, you will be responsible for ensuring that the product developed achieves business results and user satisfaction through solid and constructive management: product vision, KPI monitoring and management, roadmaps, release prioritisation and stakeholder management.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Your purpose will be to impact our clients&#39; businesses through innovative products, aligned with each client&#39;s strategic objectives.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are a Person with a Disability (PwD), please note that all vacancies at Blip are also inclusive. We look forward to receiving your application! 🚀&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The main responsibilities you will have are:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop a product evolution roadmap aligned with the client&#39;s strategic objectives, considering planned initiatives to validate hypotheses and opportunities identified through discovery.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deliver products following Blip&#39;s working methodology (software mindset), ensuring that the scope is delivered on time and with the quality expected by the client.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Plan and launch product/chatbot project releases in close collaboration with Digital Cell leaders (multidisciplinary lean/agile development teams).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Promote data-driven decision-making, maximising impact and generating value for the business.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate the understanding of project stakeholders&#39; needs and expectations through personalised and automated communication solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Guide the team in product management best practices, with a focus on lean/agile development and continuous value delivery.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Liaise directly with the customer to define strategies and enhance the success of the chatbot.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and develop a high-performance team focused on generating value for the customer.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We expect you to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be a strategist, focused on product objectives, with negotiation skills to propose and prioritise features that meet user needs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage the entire lifecycle of chatbot projects, from conception to implementation and maintenance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with multidisciplinary teams to define scope, schedule and resources.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate and facilitate meetings and workshops with customers to understand requirements, align expectations, and validate solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assess and mitigate risks, anticipating obstacles and proposing solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What are the requirements?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to lead multidisciplinary teams and foster a collaborative environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of key indicators and KPIs for product development.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communication and expectation management skills in large accounts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in agile methodologies and their ceremonies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of facilitation techniques.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience leading teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with AI applications and innovation projects.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in product and project management.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advanced Engli

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Business Development Representative (BDR) at Blip, you will play a key role in driving and growing our business. You will be the bridge between the marketing and sales teams, responsible for generating qualified sales opportunities and feeding the sales pipeline.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For this role, we are looking for someone who is agile, dynamic, proactive and results-oriented, capable of working on different challenges and with technical skills for new business development. A professional who loves sales and its challenges, knows how to communicate clearly and in an organised manner, and is eager to grow professionally within our sales team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Role in the team&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Quickly and efficiently qualify leads generated by applying pre-sales techniques and using strategic materials;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understand the needs of potential customers, providing appropriate solutions in line with Blip&#39;s business model and product;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow the Blip SLA and ensure that conversion targets are met;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor data panels and objectives;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Plan, manage, and organise tasks in HubSpot CRM;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure data is recorded in HubSpot CRM;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Map and prospect new business opportunities;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What do we expect from an BDR?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and actively prospect new potential customers through research, market analysis, and the use of sales tools.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop effective strategies to generate quality leads and maintain an up-to-date database.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Initiate and maintain effective conversations with prospects through phone calls, emails, and social media&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use specific criteria to qualify opportunities and ensure that only promising leads are pursued.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with sales representatives to transfer qualified leads and provide detailed information about each prospect.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to multitask, prioritise, and manage time efficiently.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ease of communication and integration within and outside the team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to adapt to new technologies and learn quickly.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advanced English.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;It will make a difference if you have&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience and mastery of lead prospecting techniques (outbound).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience and/or knowledge of trends in technology areas with a focus on conversational commerce;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Digital certifications in sales and marketing;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of Hubspot CRM;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in Apollo&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 data-section-id=&quot;mg9y4a&quot; data-start=&quot;92&quot; data-end=&quot;107&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sobre a Blip&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;109&quot; data-end=&quot;340&quot;&gt;Somos uma empresa global de tecnologia e líderes em&lt;strong&gt; conversational commerce&lt;/strong&gt; na América Latina, oferecendo soluções SaaS que permitem às empresas se conectarem com seus clientes por canais digitais como WhatsApp, Instagram e outros.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;342&quot; data-end=&quot;480&quot;&gt;Hoje contamos com &lt;strong&gt;mais de 1.000 colaboradores&lt;/strong&gt; e escritórios no Brasil, México e Espanha, atendendo milhares de empresas ao redor do mundo.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;482&quot; data-end=&quot;656&quot;&gt;Somos apoiados por investidores globais como Warburg Pincus, SoftBank e Microsoft, e seguimos em uma trajetória consistente de &lt;strong&gt;crescimento acelerado e expansão internacional.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 data-section-id=&quot;w1fy70&quot; data-start=&quot;663&quot; data-end=&quot;702&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sobre o Time de Product &amp;amp; Technology&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;704&quot; data-end=&quot;911&quot;&gt;Você fará parte de um time multidisciplinar que desenvolve aplicações e soluções conversacionais para clientes da Blip, atuando em parceria com pessoas desenvolvedoras, product managers e analistas de dados.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;913&quot; data-end=&quot;1094&quot;&gt;A área é guiada por uma cultura forte de produto, com abordagem &lt;strong data-start=&quot;977&quot; data-end=&quot;994&quot;&gt;design-driven&lt;/strong&gt;, onde decisões são baseadas em evidências, experimentação contínua e foco em resultados de negócio.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1096&quot; data-end=&quot;1257&quot;&gt;Nosso objetivo é criar experiências conversacionais que gerem valor real para os usuários e para o negócio, com times ágeis, autônomos e altamente colaborativos.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 data-section-id=&quot;tsg3fz&quot; data-start=&quot;1264&quot; data-end=&quot;1287&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;O que você vai fazer&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
