&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why this Role Exists&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Blip, we believe data is at the heart of our business success, powering decisions and creating value across the organization. We are looking for a dynamic and experienced Sr Data &amp;amp; Analytics Engineering Manager to lead our Data Platform, Governance, and Architecture teams. This senior leadership role is crucial in driving the development and evolution of our cutting-edge data systems while ensuring compliance, security, and scalability.&lt;/p&gt;
